ðŸ“Œ Attendance Endpoints

    Mark Attendance
        Description: Marks attendance for a player on a specific date. If already marked, returns a warning response.
        Method: POST
        URL: /attendance/mark
        Body Example:
        {
            "date": "2025-09-25",
            "present": true,
            "player": {
                "username": "atharva_sadavarte"
            }
        }

    Get Attendance for a Player
        Description: Retrieves all attendance records for a specific player.
        Method: GET
        URL: /attendance/player/{username}
        Example: /attendance/player/atharva_sadavarte

    Get Attendance by Username and Date
        Description: Retrieves a single attendance record for a given player on a specific date.
        Method: GET
        URL: /attendance/{username}/{date}
        Example: /attendance/atharva_sadavarte/2025-09-25

    Get All Attendance
        Description: Retrieves all attendance records across all players.
        Method: GET
        URL: /attendance/all    

    Remove Attendance
        Description: Removes an attendance record for the given player on the specified date.
        Method: DELETE
        URL: /attendance/remove?username={username}&date={date}
        Example: /attendance/remove?username=atharva_sadavarte&date=2025-09-25